_______________________________________________________________________________
"Judge"           
        This allows the psionicist to "look deep into another person's
        eyes and see their soul".  It will tell you how far they have
        advanced within their guild and compare their stats to yours if
        the target is a player character, and it will estimate how you
        would fare in combat against the target if it is a monster.
        Note that it judges purely from a one on one physical
        confrontation.  The psionicist has access to a host of powers
        the opponent does not and the ability to retreat and heal which
        most monster do not have.  On the other hand, some monsters
        possess special attacks or abilities which judge will also not
        factor into things.  However, it is a good way to get a general
        feeling for how tough a monster is, or how far advanced another
        player is compared to you.  
 
SP Cost:  15		Guild Level:  2		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  pjudge <target>
